DESCRIPTION:Description Join us at this restoration site along South Skagit
	 Highway near the Highway 9 bridge. From 9am-12pm we'll plant native trees
	 and shrubs to restore riparian habitat at this riverside site. These plan
	ts will help restore the Skagit River and improve habitat for salmon and m
	any other animals. Bring a club\, group and all your friends- all ages wel
	come! Please dress for the weather\, and wear shoes that can get muddy. We
